messages.subject: Really Amazing Savings & Freebies Too!
messages.msgSnippet: If you are looking to slash all your expenses by 75% then you found the right place! This is what I read several months ago when a person named Sue posted a
messages.messageBody:
If you are looking to slash all your expenses by 75% then you found
the right place! This is what I read several months ago when a person
named Sue posted a link to: http://www.wrldofproducts.com I thought
it was very interesting and decided to check it out. I am very
skeptical by nature so the first thing I did was check out the
company. I contacted the Better Business Bureau and found that the
company has had no complaints lodged against them, I also contacted
Paypal who has verified this company. They told me that they verified
the company's licenses, bank accounts and other paperwork indicating
to them that the company is legitimate. Then I started asking co-
workers and friends about this program and to my surprise 6 out of
the 10 people that I spoke with were already using this program. They
told me how pleased they were with it and how much money they had
saved and are currently saving. They told me that they have seen
numerous television programs for this. So I decided to sign up for
this program on 1/20/03. On 1/23/03 I received my complete membership
package and the fun began. Using their program and the free lifetime
membership that it includes I went to the supermarket ready to make a
killing. The cashier rang up my grocery bill and it came out to
$239.87 then I presented her with the coupons I received from this
program and I saved $223.38 - my final bill was only $16.49! The
cashier wasn't the only one shocked. Thanks Sue for sharing this
information with us!

PS: They just put an amazing section up with electronic items at
super low costs. It's worth a look.
